{"tid":580318,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「麥難民」三年增五成　九西逾四成人學歷高中以上","createTime":"2018-03-04T12:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T14:40:23.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d0c88b68310ef76a2cc90c252fffb3701a586421","tid":580318,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T12:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180304/s00001/646e46cde58445426a72cc35237b5d73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180304%2Fs00001%2F646e46cde58445426a72cc35237b5d73.jpg&h=860b209c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港租金貴，令無家者人數不斷上升；走進全日24小時營業麥當勞度宿的「麥難民」，更是日漸增加。有組織調查發現，去年全港有約384人，於通宵營業快餐店度宿，較2015年的256人，增加約五成。<br />\n<br />\n香港社區組織協會進行的「廿四小時快餐店無家者研究2018」，去年12月8日走訪港島、九龍東、九龍西及荃葵青4大區域的全日24小時營業快餐店，發現當中約有384名缺乏安定或永久居所的無家者，其中過半數（58.9%）無家者棲身九龍西，包括油尖旺及深水埗等。<br />\n<br />\n機構選取了九龍西，包括油尖旺、深水埗及九龍城共116人進行問卷調查，發現當中有逾八成九為男性，女性佔約11%，平均52.9歲，露宿時間平均達23.4個月，較2015年的18個月為多。另外，有近四成受訪者的學歷，達高中或大專以上。<br />\n<br />\n至於在通宵營業快餐店度宿原因，36.5%受訪者表示「租金太貴」；26%人則指，是由於失業無法尋找住宿。另外，有部分受訪者則是為了節省金錢（5.9%），及認為「前住環境過於惡劣」（3.9%）。<br />\n<br />\n年約63歲的Monica說，5年前曾租住劏房，惟居住環境惡劣，充滿木蝨，其後便到通宵營業快餐店度宿。由於位處室內及有冷氣供應，相對上較為舒適安全。不過，她透露留宿期間，偶然會被店員叫醒，感覺並不舒服。<br />\n<br />\n香港社區組織協會幹事吳衛東指出，近年租金水平不斷提高，建議政府重設租務管制，增加資助住宿宿位，尤其是女性宿位，並將最長6個月的居住期延長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180304/s00001/1520157633184\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180304%2Fs00001%2F1520157633184&d=fOLDslNAwYliePqxex7p76MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=a6e8bb33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180304%2Fs00001%2F1520157633184&h=f481e2df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180304/s00001/1520157633184</a>"},{"pid":"b622be7d2c9f4987d6b213b429f2a9f053bde70d","tid":580318,"uid":55568,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T12:08:59.000Z","msg":"九龍西寫做九西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊條狗西寫㗎"},{"pid":"96c9074a25c6c77e33ab953a73026a63f4e29062","tid":580318,"uid":157362,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T12:12:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4674a186804834e59e6adca29f898125146dd66","tid":580318,"uid":67338,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T12:13:25.000Z","msg":"間老麥始終唔係用黎俾你訓覺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲想點?"},{"pid":"e8461ac774e552267150de0adaa4d70fb0334973","tid":580318,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T12:14:04.000Z","msg":"住一年都慳到幾多下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87549625782ade2c3ab4a226a79b9fd02f0e7ce4","tid":580318,"uid":5006,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T12:26:18.000Z","msg":"針埋暖水你飲 濕埋毛巾比你抹身好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f28b6c348ee05402ca17c57bab363f942e9822","tid":580318,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:16:13.000Z","msg":"而家呀豬呀狗都有高中以上學歷㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e288d9d30a5e720262864680478dd52945b64d","tid":580318,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:22:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ccf42b615efa9fd2ba3b8cb235d660b4d46cd27a","tid":580318,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T14:30:32.000Z","msg":"其實金拱門現時已成偉大社會社義祖國旗下又一優秀先進文明單位，點解仲未解決到遊民問題？<br />\n<br />\n邊個失職？"},{"pid":"b75feb99f3125ac0722160ab82a5aea70c9ac6d5","tid":580318,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T14:33:53.000